Telkom has launched its Big Deal for May 2018. The deal features a SmartBroadband Wireless 10GB package and a Huawei B315 router. It features: Telkom stated that Night Surfer data is available between midnight and 07:00 every day, while the Huawei B315 router can handle speeds up to 150Mbps. It can also connect up to 32 devices. Telkom stated that the LTE data is available on the Telkom network and is non-roaming. It added that it reserves the right to throttle and/or shape the traffic of the Double Data SmartBroadband Wireless products in the network peak times between 18:00 and 23:00 daily. To see if you have Telkom LTE coverage, visit the Telkom coverage map.